      "id": "49005ef9_ffb9b235",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "message": "the code movement and everything is fine.\n\nJust an observation : \n\npreviously the jar name we were pushing was ncmp-dmi-plugin-{project-version}.jar\nand same was pushed to artifactory.\nhttps://nexus.onap.org/content/repositories/releases/org/onap/cps/ncmp-dmi-plugin/1.5.0/\n\nBut now the artifact created locally is dmi-service-{project-version}.jar\n\nBut in both the cases the image name seems to be correct.\nncmp-dmi-plugin:<tag>",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7965,
        "name": "Priyank Maheshwari",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "priyank.maheshwari@est.tech",
        "username": "mpriyank"
      },
      "updated": "2024-06-26 12:54:08.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "e781a16a_07fe1387",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "message": "The way I see is it MAY not impact anybody.\nas onap dmi plugin jar may not be pulled directly by some other application. ( maybe team opinion required )\n\nI know the docker image might be used for the deployment in OOM. ( but since we use the same name so should not impact )",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7965,
        "name": "Priyank Maheshwari",
